### Issue Fixed

`frontend/src/store.ts:1226` — The build failed with `TS2532: Object is possibly 'undefined'` because `tsconfig.app.json` enables `noUncheckedIndexedAccess`. Array index `remaining[0]` returns `T | undefined` even after a `.length > 0` guard. Fixed by assigning to `const first = remaining[0]` and checking `if (first)` before using it.

(Note: `tsc --noEmit` had passed trivially because root `tsconfig.json` has `files: []` — the strict check only runs via `tsc -b`.)

